  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Israëliteri un Wilisteri wedde tohs Karra-Pulkeus prett ween ohtru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nolikke Dahwids tohs Traukus no fewim pee ta Rihku-Sarga/ un tezzeja pee teem Karra-Pulkeem/un nahze/un apfweizinaja fawus Brahtus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu tas ar wiꞥneem runnaja/ rangi/ tad nahze tas Zihktetais aufscham/ kam tas Wahrdus bija Goliats/weens Wilisteris/ no Gattas no to Wilisteru Karra-Pulkeem/ un runnaja tohs paſchus Wahrdus/ un Dahwids dsirdeja to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet wiſti Israëka Wihri/ kad tee scho Wihru redseja/ tad behofe tee preekſch winna/ un bihjajahs fohti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Israëka Wihri fazziia: Effat juhs to Wihru redsejschi/ kas irr aufscham nahzis? Jo wiꞥsch irr nahzis Israëlu apkaunoht. Un to Wihru/ kas scho kaus/ darrihs tas Kehuitisch tohti baggatu/ un dohs tam fawu Meitu (par Seewu)/ un atlaidihs winna Tehwa Namnam to Teefu eekſch Israëka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad runnaja Dahwids us teein Wihreim/ kas pee winna stabweja/ un fazziia: Kas taps tam Wihram darrihts/ kas scho Wilisteri kaus/ un to Kan-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad stahstija wiꞥnam t Laudischohs paſchus Wahrdus un fazziia: ta un ta taps tam Wihram darrihts/ kas wiꞥnakans.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad dsirdeja Eliabś winna leelakajs Brahlis winnu teen Wihreem runnajam/ un Eliabs apſkaitehs pahr Dahwidun fazziia: Kapelz tad effi tu lejā nahzis? un pee ka effi tu to mettis? Es gann finnu tawu Lelibu/ un tawu Sirds Blehdibu Jo tu effi nahzis to Kaufchanredſeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazziia Dahwids/ tad nu es etmu darrijs? woj mate ne bij jadarra?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥsch greesehs no pee zitta/ un fazziia schohs paſchus Wahrdus. Un tee Laudathildeja tam lihds ka pirnak.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu fchee Wahrditape dsirdeti/ ko Dahwids runnajun preekſch Saula runnati tape/ tad likke wiꞥsch to atwest.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids fazziia u Saulu: Laid ne weenain ta Sirsfuhd winna pehz. Taws Kalpno-ees/un kaufeis ar scho Wilister\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Sauls fazziia u Dahwidu: Tu ne warrefi no-eeprett scho Wilisteri/ ar winnkantees. Bet tueff weens Puifis\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
